            "jpText": "『日本ダービー』を制したキングヘイロー。\r\nウイナーズ・サークルで高笑いをあげたのも\n束の間。彼女は取材陣の前から姿を消す。",
            "enText": "King Halo won the Japan Derby. Her laughter was \nonly heard from the winner's circle for a \nbrief time. She disappeared from the press.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 125,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 136,
                    "pathId": -711342672577454308
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 136,
                    "pathId": -6820986443246907402
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7116563275684767581,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……敗北して悔し涙を流している\r\nスペシャルウィークから、\n取材陣の目をそらすために。",
            "enText": "To distract the reporters from Special \nWeek, who was crying tears of frustration \nafter losing…",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 101,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 14,
                    "pathId": -2171611867200772953
                },
