                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1499370068522714587,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "レース後、電話が鳴る。それはスペシャル\r\nウィークの走りを称え、キングヘイローの\n勝利後の行動を咎める母からの電話だった。",
            "enText": "After the race, there was a call. It was her \nmother, praising Special Week and criticising \nKing Halo's behavior after her victory.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 124,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 158,
                    "pathId": -1147287861008770520
                },
                {
