            "pathId": -5263726356630634974,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……まだ、認められないならば。\r\nキングヘイローはクラシック三冠路線の最後\n『菊花賞』でも結果を残すと誓ったのだった。",
            "enText": "… She still won't accept her. King Halo vowed \nto leave her mark on the final race of the \nTriple Crown Classic, Kikka Sho, as well.",
